{% include '@meganav' %}
<div class="masthead">
  <div class="masthead__inner">
    <div class="masthead__bg">
      <img src="{{ ('/img/masthead' ~ random(4) ~ '.jpg') | path }}"/>
    </div>
    <div class="wrap">
      {% include '@breadcrumbs' %}
      {% include '@title' with {
        text: 'Student Life',
        modifiers: ['has-tail'],
        textElement: 'h1',
        animate: true
      } %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<main id="main-content" role="main" class="">

  <div class="slab  slab--bg-offwhite">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="intro">Stand out from the crowd by making the most of your time at university. There’s so much potential at Staffordshire University to explore and so many new things to try. You’ll have fun times, make new friends and
        create memories for life.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="slab">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="title  title--has-tail  js-waypoint">
        <h2 class="title__highlight">Features and highlights</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid  grid-2-cols">
        <div>
          <a class="feature-link" href="">
            <figure class="feature-link__figure">
              <img src="https://placeimg.com/720/360" alt=""/>
            </figure>

            <div class="feature-link__content">
              <h3 class="h4 feature-link__title">Accommodation</h3>
              <p>Where you live is a big part of your student experience and where you’ll meet friends for life.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <a class="feature-link" href="">
            <figure class="feature-link__figure">
              <img src="https://placeimg.com/720/360" alt=""/>
            </figure>

            <div class="feature-link__content">
              <h3 class="h4 feature-link__title">Life in Staffordshire</h3>
              <p>We’ve invested in great new facilities on campus to make Staffordshire University a hub of activity and opportunity.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <a class="feature-link" href="">
            <div class="feature-link__content">
              <h3 class="h4 feature-link__title">Getting involved</h3>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <a class="feature-link" href="">
            <div class="feature-link__content">
              <h3 class="h4 feature-link__title">Campus & facilities</h3>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <a class="feature-link" href="">
            <div class="feature-link__content">
              <h3 class="h4 feature-link__title">Student support</h3>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <a class="feature-link" href="">
            <div class="feature-link__content">
              <h3 class="h4 feature-link__title">Life on campus</h3>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% include '@banner--align-full' %}

  <div class="slab">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="title  title--has-tail  js-waypoint">
        <h2 class="title__highlight">The voice of our students</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Don't just take our word for it. Hear what our students have to say through their own vlogs or by chatting to them directly.</p>


      <div class="grid  grid--spaced">
        <div class="col-3/4">
          <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/p6XAlr9jGFI" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="col-1/4">
          <div class="box  box--bg-slate  box--padded">Another variation of card?</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


</main>

{% include '@slider--accolades' %}
{% include '@page-footer' %}